4#include <QtCore/QString>
5#include <QtCore/QStringList>
6#include <memory>
7namespace QtNodes
8{
9 using NodeDataTypeId = QString;
10 class NodeDataType
11 {
12 public:
13 NodeDataType() = default;
14 virtual ~NodeDataType() = default;
15 NodeDataType(const QString &id, const QString &name) : _id(id), _name(name)
16 {
17 }
18 virtual bool operator==(const NodeDataType &other) const
19 {
20 return id() == other.id();
21 }
22 virtual bool operator!=(const NodeDataType &other) const
23 {
24 return !(*this == other);
25 }
26 virtual bool operator<(const NodeDataType &other) const
27 {
28 return id() < other.id();
29 }
30 NodeDataTypeId id() const
31 {
32 return _id;
33 }
34 QString name() const
35 {
36 return _name;
37 }
38
39 private:
40 NodeDataTypeId _id;
41 QString _name;
42 };
43 /// Class represents data transferred between nodes.
44 /// @param type is used for comparing the types
45 /// The actual data is stored in subtypes
46 class NODE_EDITOR_PUBLIC NodeData
47 {
48 public:
49 virtual ~NodeData() = default;
50 virtual bool sameType(NodeData const &nodeData) const
51 {
52 return (this->type() == nodeData.type());
53 }
54 /// Type for inner use
55 virtual std::shared_ptr<NodeDataType> type() const = 0;
56 };
57} // namespace QtNodes
